        "html": "<p>Hey {first_name, \"there\"},</p><p>So, welcome to the first post of the third decade of <em>One Man &amp; His Blog</em>. What a terrifying statement that is, but it‚Äôs true after this site <a href=\"__GHOST_URL__/2023/03/20-years-of-one-man-his-blog/\">hit its 20th anniversary</a> over the weekend.&nbsp;</p><p>Let's not dwell on that. No, let's take some time to look at wahat's happening on newer platforms, like YouTube (two years younger than this site) and LinkedIn (two months younger‚Ä¶).</p><p>Oh, God, I'm old, aren't I?</p>"
